{"tid":122054,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"判傷一問","createTime":"2017-02-15T17:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T22:13:04.000Z","uid":37325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"288c44e1c5b51012f08b1372ff6d0f2a621afae0","tid":122054,"uid":37325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:18:24.000Z","msg":"小弟今年廿零歲，係個裝修佬，因為有日係梯上面失重心仆落地下跌斷隻腳，抖左幾個月，每日都有八成人工 (老闆話係佢比住我先 到時先扣返)，但八成人工嘅金額已經超過左判傷所賠嘅錢，呢家佢問我拎返，係未要比返佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢家我月入先萬五，個差額都成三皮幾四皮，未要我on99白做返比佢  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08bac95fa680db3a136e73c618d79a929f4c5ec","tid":122054,"uid":37325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:38:39.000Z","msg":"無助求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720d1e9e977d1161a7c5149ab60793e83826b71e","tid":122054,"uid":64648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:56:49.000Z","msg":"打去勞工處問"},{"pid":"c5dfb445e9bfcedb9034ed747e08b65dc8bdaa60","tid":122054,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:58:52.000Z","msg":"工傷喎"},{"pid":"0eb47066883877ba69ae563310fcdefe4543eadb","tid":122054,"uid":38206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T22:13:04.000Z","msg":"你可以上訴個%<br />\n你而家冇病假啦?你其實可以keep住拎病假claim錢，醫療費都可以claim返<br />\n另外你有冇野覺得係公司疏忽令你發生意外?有就另外又可以要佢賠償，車費補品都claim得，申請legal aid 搵律師行告佢，拎返十幾廿十萬"}]}